{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_03_03",
  "title": "川咲さくら 3話 ハッピーニューイヤー！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "明けましておめでとうございまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year‚ everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 3.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "私達の新春ライブに来てくれてありがとう！\nサニーピースがお正月を盛り上げるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for coming to our New Year's live!\nSunny Peace will liven up the New Year!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6300,
          "startTime": 10
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 12.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "新しい年をみんなと迎えられて凄く幸せ！\nこれからの一年もサニーピースをよろしくね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so happy to welcome the new year with everyone!\nPlease continue to support Sunny Peace this year too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7266.666666599999,
          "startTime": 19.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの今年の抱負は何かな？　私の抱負は……\n楽しいことやワクワクすることをいっぱいやります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are everyone's resolutions for this year? As for mine…\nI'll do lots of fun and exciting things!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 32
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ハッピーニューイヤー！　笑う門には福来るだよ！\nみんな笑顔で、ハッピーな一年にしようね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year! Good fortune will come to those who smile!\nLet's all have a happy and smile-filled year!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 41.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 41.7
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 41.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、お正月にふさわしい\n明るくて元気に溢れたいいライブだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job‚ that was a lively and\nenergetic live show‚ perfect for New Year's.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 48.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\n沢山の人が観に来てくれて私も気持ち良く歌えました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!\nThere were so many people who came to watch‚ and it made me feel great while singing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "ところで{user}さん\nこの後なんですけど、予定は空いてますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ {user}-san‚\ndo you have any plans after this? Are you free?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 61.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "特に急ぎの用事はないが……どうかしたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't have any urgent plans‚ but… is there something you need?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 66.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "それなら一つお願いがあるんですけどいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ I have one favor to ask. Is it okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 71.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n私に、付き合って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nWill you‚ accompany me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 79.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 79.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "付き合ってほしいって言うから何事かと思えば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wondered what it was when you said you wanted me to accompany…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、この後ホットドッグさんと対決するので\n本番前に羽根つきの練習をしておきたかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ but I have a match with Mr.Hot Dog after this‚\nso I wanted to practice Hanetsuki before the live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 92.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いくらでも練習相手になるけど、また俺に負けて\n自信を無くしても責任は取れないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be your practice partner as many times as you want‚\nbut if you lose again‚ I can't take responsibility‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "言いましたね～！　私だって負けませんから！\nこてんぱんにしちゃいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said that before~! But I won't lose either!\nI will destroy you~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 105.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、いきますよ！　せーのーー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here we go! Ready‚ set‚ go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ！　しまった、またやられた！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no! I lost!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "やりました、また私の勝ちです！\nこれで私の三連勝ですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did it! I won again!\nThat's three wins in a row for me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、顔を出して下さい\nじっとして、動いちゃダメですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ show me your face now.\nStay still‚ don't move.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～、また落書き出来るなんて\n悪い子になった気分です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe~! I can't believe\nI get to draw on your face again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "墨を顔に塗るのには魔除けの意味があるらしいですよ\nこれで今年一年、健康に過ごせる……かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They say putting ink on your face is a charm\nto keep you healthy for the year… I wonder if it'll work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "お正月の遊びっていいですね、勝った人も負けた人も\nみんな笑顔になれるから大好きです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "New Year's playtime is so much fun. Everyone‚ winners and losers‚\ngets to smile‚ and I love that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 153.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いやぁ、まいった\n見違えるほどうまくなったじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geez‚ I give up.\nYou've improved so much‚ it's incredible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 160.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "前はホットドッグさんと共演するって言われて\nカチコチになるくらい緊張してたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before‚ I used to get extremely nervous\nwhen I was told I'd be performing with Mr.Hot Dog…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "みんなとお正月を楽しんでリフレッシュしたおかげで\n今日は肩の力が抜けて調子がいいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But thanks to enjoying New Year's with everyone\nand refreshing my mind‚ I feel more relaxed now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 174.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "ライブも大成功だったし\n今なら何をやっても負ける気がしません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live show was a big success‚ too.\nRight now‚ I feel like I won't lose no matter what I do!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "この調子なら本番でもいい勝負が出来そうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this rate‚ you might put up a good fight in the main performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 184.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
