      "text": "はい！　あ……でもあまり上手だと\nバラエティ番組としては盛り上がらないでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! But‚ uh… if I'm too good‚\nit might not be as entertaining for a variety show‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
