      "text": "お笑い業界は爪痕を残してなんぼ……\nむしろ下手な方がお笑い業界で生き残れるかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the comedy industry‚ leaving a mark is everything…\nMaybe being bad is better for surviving in the comedy industry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
